text: Musa tana jativarito ila annadu: " Allah miku cesina anugrahalanu jnapakam cesukondi. Ayana miku phir'aun jativari nundi vimukti kaligincadu. Varu mim'malni tivramaina siksalaku guricestu undevaru, mi kumarulanu vadhinci, mi kumartelanu (strilanu) bratakaniccevaru. Mariyu andulo miku, mi prabhuvu tarapu nundi oka goppa pariksa undindi
